{"tid":675025,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 重新受到年輕族群青睞，MS 希望更多用家愛上 Windows","createTime":"2018-05-23T08:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T05:02:12.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"09f763754adaab12c06acf1cc880781a64c96084","tid":675025,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"早在 2015 年，微軟（Microsoft）執行長薩蒂亞 &middot; 納德拉（Satya Nadella）就曾表示，微軟最大的目標是希望讓需要使用 Windows 作業系統的用戶，能先喜歡上 Windows 最後再愛上它<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。經過幾年的努力，Satya Nadella 的目標似乎成真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。據外媒《YouGov》的調查，近年群眾對 Windows 的喜愛似乎有正向成長的趨勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/155731_b3ee0409e9a8f013ce5f5008cae81e60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F155731_b3ee0409e9a8f013ce5f5008cae81e60.png&h=b9e99bcc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n《YouGov BrandIndex》的數據調查顯示，消費者對於微軟的品牌印象分數在過去幾個星期內達到了高點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。在 CEO 納德拉宣布將重組公司部門以及針對 Windwos 10 推出更新的時間點，微軟的印象分數更從 36 升到 40 個百分點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2018/05/21/180521-33652-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F180521-33652-2.jpg&h=f2d6de81&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n其中，美國年輕族群對於微軟的興趣最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，18-34 歲的年輕人平均給了微軟 44 分，比起 35 歲以上的 39 多出 15%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2018/05/21/180521-33652-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F180521-33652-3.jpg&h=3e7cde1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/33652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F33652&d=c%2BJMtgH2msu1T9K6ZL12azANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=da5f65fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F33652&h=af87b4f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/33652</a></div>"},{"pid":"746b290b650757c9a5f0de53cdd8f6e755788a52","tid":675025,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"微軟近年也積極拓展雲端業務，這可能也影響了年輕人對微軟的觀感。相比之下，35 歲以上的族群則認僅有 39% 的人信任雲端技術。<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，對微軟保持樂觀態度的消費者，也比其他人更相信 AI 人工智慧在未來能替人類處理大部分日常事務。"},{"pid":"5e423314b7642655e6e4fe7316dba1f9a718ad06","tid":675025,"uid":52194,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:03:58.000Z","msg":"Surface都拎得岀街見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e547ff7c56ccbd2f53de0161221271ae589f5ba2","tid":675025,"uid":89514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:06:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb86d248d0bd27b3aece1573d62a885af5b8107b","tid":675025,"uid":10009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"Marketing 唔係淨靠上黎軟件台鳩叫人用linux就得<br />\n宣傳？倒米就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23851daa536ab46a98d45883c85b35c5bf47a53","tid":675025,"uid":25825,"like":0